The functionality of the comviva for the oredoo is the technical, sales and pm.

Rest Api, Gui interface and bulk batch processing of the files.

Rest Api over the HTTPS method using the post method.

Request can be fulfilled by the SYNC AND ASYNC methods
SYNC -> request comes in and the problem resolvtion is done on the priority basis
ASYNC -> in this the request comes in and once the acknowledgement is done then the actions are taken accordingly.

